			"Duration": "1 day",
			"Save": "None",
			"Description": "<p>By means of this spell, the caster grants himself increased powers of memory with regard to spells.</p><p>The caster has two options, which he can choose between at Casting Time:</p><ol><li>Memorise additional spells, up to three additional spell levels (three 1st-level spells, one 1st and one 2nd, or one 3rd-level spell). The additional spells must then be memorised normally.</li><li>Recall to memory any spell of 1st-4th level. The chosen spell must have been cast within the last hour. This restores the previously cast spell to the wizard and allows them to cast it again.</li></ol><p><em>Nystul</em>, the creator of the spell, is most famous for tutoring <em>Mordenkainen</em> 'the Master' as a youth. Mordenkainen based his own spell, <em class=\"spell\">Mordenkainen's Lucubration</em>, on this work.</p>"
