			"Range": "0",
			"AOE": "See below",
			"Duration": "5 rounds / caster level",
			"Save": "None",
			"Description": "<p>This spell is an improved version of <em class=\"spell\">Shield</em>. It creates a mobile barrier that remains in front of the caster to help protect him against harm.</p><p>This <em class=\"spellname\">Bulwark</em> totally negates <em class=\"spell\">Magic Missiles</em>. It provides the equivalent protection of AC 1 against hurled missiles (e.g axes, darts, javelins, spears), AC 2 against small propelled missiles (e.g arrows, bolts, manticore spikes, sling stones), and AC 3 against all other forms of attack. The <em class=\"spellname\">Bulwark</em> also adds a +2 bonus to the wizard's Saves.</p><p>These benefits apply only if the attacks originate from in front of the wizard, where the <em class=\"spellname\">Bulwark</em> can shift to interpose itself.</p>"
