		"school": "Abjuration",
		"Casting Time": "30 minutes",
			"Range": "0",
			"AOE": "Caster only",
			"Duration": "See below",
			"Save": "See below",
			"Description": "<p>This spell requires the caster to inscribe a series of protective sigils upon their skin, using a mixture of inks made from powdered amethyst, toad blood and fennel leaves. These marks can be later covered by armour or clothing, if wanted. When complete, the magic surrounds the wizard with an aura that provides immunity to arcane curses of 4th level or below.</p><p>The aura not only protects, it causes curses to rebound upon their casters. The caster can resist their own curses by making a Save, if the curse allows it. Otherwise they take full effect.</p><p>If multiple creatures are targeted by a curse, <em class=\"spellname\">Rebound Curses</em> protects only the caster.</p><p><em class=\"spellname\">Rebound Curses</em> is effective upon all of the following:</p><ul><li><em class=\"spell\">Curse Of Shapes</em></li><li><em class=\"spell\">Curse Of The Medusae</em></li><li><em class=\"spell\">Dolorous Itch</em></li><li><em class=\"spell\">Hargyn's Uncontrollable Hideous Laughter</em></li><li><em class=\"spell\">Insatiable Thirst</em></li><li><em class=\"spell\">Sleep</em></li><li><em class=\"spell\">Strike Blind</em></li><li><em class=\"spell\">Strike Deaf</em></li><li><em class=\"spell\">Strike Dumb</em></li><li><em class=\"spell\">Undeniable Oblivion</em></li><li><em class=\"spell\">Wizard's Curse</em></li><li><em class=\"spell\">Wizard's Curse, Lesser</em></li><li><em class=\"spell\">Wizard's Curse, Greater</em></li><li><em class=\"spell\">Ylfe-Shot</em></li></ul><p>This magic does not affect priestly curses. While it is in effect, the caster loses a 6th-level spell 'slot'.</p>"
	},
