		"title": "Spectral Hand",
		"level": 2,
		"school": "Conjuration",
		"Casting Time": "2",
			"Range": "90 ft. + 15 ft. / caster level",
			"AOE": "See below",
			"Duration": "2 rounds / caster level",
			"Save": "None",
			"Description": "<p>This spell causes a ghostly, immaterial <em class=\"spellname\">Hand</em> to materialize within the spell range and move as the caster desires. Any touch attack spell of 4th level or less that is subsequently cast by the wizard can be delivered by the <em class=\"spellname\">Spectral Hand</em>, with a +2 bonus to the attack roll.</p><p>The caster cannot perform any other actions when attacking with the <em class=\"spellname\">Hand</em>; it returns to hover by the caster's side if the caster takes other actions.</p><p>The <em class=\"spellname\">Hand</em> receives flank and rear attack bonuses if the caster is in a position to do so. It is vulnerable to magical attack, including from enchanted weapons, with an AC of 2. Any damage to the <em class=\"spellname\">Spectral Hand</em> ends the spell and inflicts 1d4 HP damage to the caster.</p><p>If the caster dies, the <em class=\"spellname\">Hand</em> vanishes within moments.</p>"
