			"Range": "Touch",
			"AOE": "Person touched",
			"Duration": "10 minutes / caster level",
			"Save": "None",
			"Description": "<p>An application of this spell fills the recipient's muscles with a vibrant and exhilarating fervour, increasing their Strength.</p><p>The Strength gained depends on the caster's level, as shown below:</p><dl class=\"simple\"><dt>3rd</dt><dd>16</dd><dt>4th</dt><dd>17</dd><dt>5th</dt><dd>18</dd><dt>6th</dt><dd>18/01</dd><dt>7th</dt><dd>18/75</dd><dt>8th</dt><dd>18/00</dd><dt>9th or more</dt><dd>19</dd></dl><p>Those with Strength already greater than the granted value gain +1 (or +50% Extraordinary) instead.</p><p>Creatures without Strength scores receive a +1 to attack and damage rolls.</p><p>Neither <em class=\"spell\">Permanency</em> nor a <em class=\"spell\">Wish</em> can make the gain permanent.</p>"
