			"Description": "<p>This spell is a more powerful version of <em class=\"spell\">Burning Hands</em>, producing an intensely bright fan of searing flames from the caster's hands, which must be held outstretched with the thumbs touching.</p><p>The flames inflict 1d6 HP damage, +3 / caster level, to a maximum of 1d6 + 30. A target who Saves takes half damage. Flammable materials touched by the fire begin to burn; such materials can be extinguished in the next round if no other action is taken.</p>"
