			"Save": "None",
			"Description": "<p>A <em class=\"spellname\">Wizard Lock</em> cast upon a door, chest, lock or portal magically secures it.</p><p>The caster can freely pass his own <em class=\"spellname\">Lock</em> without affecting it; otherwise, the secured object can only be opened by physically breaking it, by a successful <em class=\"spell\">Dispel Arcane Magic</em>, or by <em class=\"spell\">Knock</em>. Note that <em class=\"spell\">Knock</em> does not remove the <em class=\"spellname\">Wizard Lock</em>; it only negates it for five minutes.</p>"
